y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02376b4dd842fe6b41e87b82c28884d665e7268","tid":631014,"uid":43518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:30:46.000Z","msg":"你無你想像中咁鐘意佢囉<br />\n你寧願同朋友見面，都唔想陪佢<br />\n其實證明佢係你心入面唔係真係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下 你每次見到佢 第一下個感覺係咩"},{"pid":"a709096f1bb259364190e6c931f0ff9c695b8691","tid":631014,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93cace54e0c2cb8b26b2ba14aef1a67618de971c","tid":631014,"uid":21473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"你自己都有答案啦,根本唔會因為咁少事分開<br />\n但如果你自己心態KEEP住係咁諗<br />\n你根本唔會拍到長拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖,心態最重要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"我知道咁落去唔係辦法 <br />\n我應該點樣去改變個心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377ca77ec0d8b2483a6dd62c130af0a8617fffd3","tid":631014,"uid":180964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9aec2ef2a1297a7357f49e6eb465429afb23de19","tid":631014,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"呢排唔知係唔係因為多野做 見小左 三日見一次咁<br />\n就算見到都無左之前個種好興奮開心既感覺<br />\n有時鬧交都已經唔想再鬧 即刻應低威咁 <br />\n更加鍾意同朋友相處既時間多啲比起陪佢<br />\n到底我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲都試過咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"幾時淡埋右？"},{"pid":"80a5720eb0eed537b8fc35999e1691de3acd5360","tid":631014,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16cf86763d6702e403148becb4ae83594caeabfe","tid":631014,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4806916ac42295f1e90690c5487e0d39c5c871","tid":631014,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"無feel啊。。分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"小小野就要分手？<